      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">The tiny slime is useless and inert until an intellect generates an electromagnetic field of the right wavelength and of sufficient force to drive it to purpose. While holding its stone, its keeper can direct it telepathically and have the slime imitate any shape they desire as a bonus action, however it remains a Tiny creature.</span></p>",
